            "creation_date": 1278647650,
            "body": "<p>Check the documentation/FAQ for your driver. For example, if you're using Oracle's driver, these may help:<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technology/tech/java/sqlj_jdbc/htdocs/jdbc_faq.html#32_00\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Oracle JDBC Trace Facility<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technology/tech/java/sqlj_jdbc/htdocs/jdbc_faq.html#36_00\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">java.util.logging<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>If you're using the WebLogic driver:<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/docs/cd/E14571_01/web.1111/e13753/spy.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Tracking JDBC Calls with WebLogic JDBC Spy<\/a><\/p>\n",
